channel.title: [Request] The original log-in box and buttons [Request]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I've been searching google and this forum for the original log in box and titlebox. Here's an example if you still dont know what I mean.:
[img]http://holdenrules64.files.wordpress.com/2007/01/runescape-login1.png[/img]
Like that one, but I only need the Titlebox.png or .jpg, and the Titlebutton.png or .jpg.
Please help me out, would really appriciate it, Thanks.
